<codeline><highlight class="normal">1.<sp/>**Fluent<sp/>Interface**:<sp/>Method<sp/>chaining<sp/>for<sp/>readable<sp/>configuration.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">2.<sp/>**Callback-Based<sp/>Configuration**:<sp/>Builders<sp/>are<sp/>configured<sp/>via<sp/>lambdas,<sp/>allowing<sp/>scoped<sp/>access.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">3.<sp/>**Automatic<sp/>Dependencies**:<sp/>Configs<sp/>automatically<sp/>add<sp/>required<sp/>dependent<sp/>components.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">4.<sp/>**Separation<sp/>of<sp/>Concerns**:<sp/>Each<sp/>builder<sp/>focuses<sp/>on<sp/>a<sp/>single<sp/>domain<sp/>(motion,<sp/>rendering,<sp/>etc.).</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">5.<sp/>**Cloning<sp/>Support**:<sp/>`GameObjectFactory::from()`<sp/>creates<sp/>new<sp/>entities<sp/>based<sp/>on<sp/>existing<sp/>templates.</highlight></codeline>
